This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves the use of neural networks for translation. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves the use of machine learning techniques for language translation. The paper also mentions the use of statistical machine translation, which could place it under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as these sub-categories also deal with statistical modeling and pattern recognition.
